Headline: AACS Graduation Fashion Show
News Content: AACS Graduation Fashion Show - Graduation Model Show - 2016 – 3RD Edition was concluded successfully on 30th November 2016 at Galadari Hotel, Colombo with the award presentation followed by an after party. It was an outstanding event as a batch of young fresh fashion designers have launched and was awarded for their inspired talents. The event has intended to give an extraordinary yet unforgettable experience to the audience in every perspective than the 1st and 2nd editions.
